room_title: Escape room "Mission's Breakout: the Ultimate Bank Heist" by Mission Escape Games in Los Angeles
room_description: You’ve gotten mixed up in the wrong crowd and it’s time to pay your debt! The mob wants you to clear it by getting them what they want. You have one hour to retrieve a rare artifact stored in the bank vault before it’s too late. Do you have what it takes to pull off The Ultimate Bank Heist?
